OBJECTIVE: protect SUPPLIES till end of alien attack.

 in this mission< you will be deployed in a series of rooms
where 2 equipment caches are located. aliens will attempt to
break into the complex from the cave system outside @ destroy
the supplies. prevent them from breaking in.
            -----------------------------------
PICKING UP EQUIPMENT: when the cursor is on an equipment item
 it will change to a hand. left click to pick it up. if you
 are standing on a piece of equipment< click on the marine to
 pick it up. you can also use the fourth icon on the icon bar
 to either pick an item up< or if you are not standing on an
 item of equipment< it will drop the currently selected item.

USING LIFTS: stand in the lift and face the green button on
 the floor. then OPERATE using the icon or pressing >Q>/>Y>.
  if the lift shaft is empty  then use the red button to call
 another one - it will arrive after a few seconds. if debris
 covers a button< it cannot be used.

AUTO ROTATION: >F>/>L> - if a trooper is needed to cover more
 than one direction in >auto> mode< use this key. face in 1
 of the desired directions @ press this key. a red arrow will
 appear. rotate to the other direction @ press again. the 
 marine will switch to auto @ rotate between these positions.
            -----------------------------------
    when the mission is complete< use the LIFT to exit.

 -      arrows       :-              - main alien assault. -
 -   silver stars    :-              - supply caches.      -
 -     zone >c>      :-              - lift.               -
